The paper discusses the secure storage and management of logs in IoT devices, which involves aspects of cryptography, information retrieval, database management, networking, and software engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.DB (Databases), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
